  "name": "CAIAC Auth - Change Password v1.0.0",
  "active": true,
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## CAIAC Auth - Change Password v1.0.0\n\n**Trigger:** POST /caiac/auth/change-password\n**Auth:** Bearer token + HMAC via [Utility] Validate Auth v1.0.0\n\n**Required headers:**\n- `Authorization: Bearer {token}`\n- `X-Webhook-Secret`\n- `X-CAIAC-Timestamp`\n- `X-CAIAC-Signature`\n\n**Flow:**\n1. Receive `{ current_password, new_password }`\n2. Validate auth via sub-workflow (401 on fail)\n3. Fetch current password_hash from DB\n4. bcrypt verify current password (401 if wrong)\n5. bcrypt hash new password\n6. UPDATE users SET password_hash, must_change_password=false\n7. 200 { success: true }\n\n**Depends on:** `/bcrypt/verify` and `/bcrypt/hash` on caiac_api.py (172.18.0.1:8000)",
        "height": 360,
        "width": 460,
        "color": 6
      },
      "id": "ad939f0f-13fe-433f-b17a-4cfdfbecdd6f",
      "name": "About This Workflow",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [0, 0]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "caiac/auth/change-password",
        "responseMode": "responseNode",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "99670ebf-21b5-49fb-8844-ec5d5ce7ee5e",
      "name": "Receive Request",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 2.1,
      "position": [0, 448],
      "webhookId": "5857a04a-20e4-43b8-99c7-74231ae49b8b"
    },
    {
      "id": "prepare-auth-inputs-cp",
      "name": "Prepare Auth Inputs",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [160, 448],
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const req = $input.first().json;\nreturn [{ json: {\n  token: (req.headers.authorization || '').replace(/^Bearer\\s+/i, ''),\n  timestamp: req.headers['x-caiac-timestamp'],\n  signature: req.headers['x-caiac-signature']\n} }];"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "call-full-auth-cp",
      "name": "Call Full Auth",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.executeWorkflow",
